name: Forest Kitty
description:
In a dark world full of thorns, an unlikely friendship is going to bloom. Enter the dark forest, jump and climb to avoid any obstacles that are standing in your way to your little friend. But remember some cats maybe have 9 lives, but others may not be so lucky.

Forest Kitty is a short but challanging platformer game, made for Mini Jam 127: Cats
